{"tid":1505435,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯高呼「掃走黑勢力！」 促追究曾參予罷課學校","createTime":"2019-08-25T14:11:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T15:34:30.000Z","uid":51665,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"37e17504c5c2e2460f5f634b564a29c287c74be2","tid":1505435,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:11:21.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯表示，要打擊九月初的罷課，先要追究曾參予罷課的七十多間學校，要其管理層問責。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯昨在微博大曬粉絲送給他的禮物，並揚言「讓我們團結一致，擊退港獨，掃走黑勢力！」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯亦在facebook發帖，指「所謂反送中民陣友，其實都是傀儡，是美國利益的二打六打手，在香港只有一個目標，就是反中亂港」，又說「港獨？香港人加油？他們就是愛誤導一些無知少男少女或一部份超齢（齡）白痴！」<br />\n<br />\n何君堯今日接受香港衛視專訪，認為要打擊九月初開學的罷課，就先要追究六月十二日曾參予罷課的七十多間學校，要校方管理層問責。<br />\n<br />\n他又要求律政司強硬檢控暴動，給予警方更多人力及法律支援，令警員執法時更具「底氣」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=7104977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D7104977&d=06o7JzqVhDqA6Aam%2BaIp81%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=48726e8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=7104977</a><br />\n未fc唔知真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1117f68d74794a7619f159001f1f714234ac9b","tid":1505435,"uid":106336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:16:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文革式批鬥</span></span></em></strong></div>"},{"pid":"378dde5cba8ad5276d5f1a39d8d8dcd928febfef","tid":1505435,"uid":188374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T14:30:59.000Z","msg":"你咪黑勢力囉 話自己？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8506d3ed437b39c83ad0f525d933a6e722f937d","tid":1505435,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:27:37.000Z","msg":"何妖自己消失先啦<br />\n黑勢力"},{"pid":"8c579b5e490f78d72df0f1a4396f5d624ba74c07","tid":1